      <text class="text-lg">
       With over a decade of experience in <b>digital marketing</b>, I specialize in driving results through SEO, Google Ads, Local Services Ads, and various other cutting-edge strategies. My expertise lies in creating tailored campaigns that boost online visibility, generate quality leads, and deliver measurable ROI. Whether it's optimizing websites for search engines or crafting impactful ad campaigns, I am passionate about helping businesses grow and succeed in the digital space.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="https://twitter.com/uncle_segun" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
